{"type": "article", "id": 29426, "title": "混凝土摇椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-11T23:01:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160711174046UJGNfYLqQ9RVgD4v.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>法国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.lyon-beton.com/\">Lyon Béton</a> 一向以制作混凝土家具见长，最近 Henri Lavallard Boget 和 Julie Legros 携手打造了名为 Hauteville 的座椅系列，设计原型来源于 Boget 在废弃建筑物中发现的一把 50 年代的座椅。这个系列正在不断开发当中，全部采用混凝土和钢筋制作而成。Hauteville 的最新迭代款是一把摇椅，采用了符合人体工程学的造型设计，豪放又不失优雅。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.lyon-beton.com/store/concrete-furniture/hauteville-rocking-chair/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 594.79 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711174203dw6xXJUrl0yjzHef.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711174204TaycFxmJHeMbNDWl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607111742048jPaSGg7WL3Oo0RJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.512225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160711174210v7G8dRXjo0SyDmk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}